ZH: 这只狗是东墙上的害群之马。
EN: This dog is the black sheep of the east wall.

ZH: 妈妈总是说我是家里的害群之马。
EN: Mom always says that I am the black sheep of the family.

ZH: 我们组里有一个害群之马总是拖后腿。
EN: There is a black sheep in our group who is always lagging behind.

ZH: 警察在抓捕害群之马时受了伤。
EN: The police got injured while capturing the black sheep.

ZH: 这个员工是公司的害群之马。
EN: This employee is the black sheep of the company.

ZH: 那个队员对球队造成了害群之马。
EN: That team member is causing trouble for the team.

ZH: 他被认为是害群之马的理由是他经常迟到。
EN: He is considered the black sheep because he is always late.

ZH: 公司里有一个害群之马正在泄露机密信息。
EN: There is a black sheep in the company leaking confidential information.

ZH: 这只猫是这个公园的害群之马。
EN: This cat is the black sheep of the park.

ZH: 那位领导被认为是部门的害群之马。
EN: That leader is seen as the black sheep of the department.

ZH: 他被认为是学校里的害群之马，因为他欺负同学。
EN: He is considered the black sheep of the school because he bullies his classmates.

ZH: 她是我们办公室的害群之马，总是拖后腿。
EN: She is the black sheep of our office, always falling behind.

ZH: 那只鸟在宠物店被称为宅群之马因为它打架。
EN: The bird in the pet store is called the black sheep because it fights.

ZH: 我们应该警惕那些害群之马，以免他们伤害我们。
EN: We should be vigilant of those black sheep, so they don't harm us.

ZH: 家庭中的害群之马可以给整个家庭带来不好的影响。
EN: The black sheep in a family can bring negative impacts to the whole household.

ZH: 在班上有一个害群之马总是制造混乱。
EN: There is a black sheep in the class who always causes chaos.

ZH: 公司中的害群之马往往影响整个团队的氛围。
EN: The black sheep in the company often affects the atmosphere of the entire team.

ZH: 这个社区有个害群之马正在引起麻烦。
EN: There is a black sheep in this community causing trouble.

ZH: 在团队中，一个害群之马可以破坏整个团队的合作精神。
EN: In a team, a black sheep can disrupt the spirit of cooperation.

ZH: 他是团队中的害群之马，因为他总是独自行动。
EN: He is the black sheep of the team because he always acts alone.
